com.github.wuic.exception

Interface ErrorCode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BadArgumentException, BadClassException, BuilderPropertyNotSupportedException, BuilderPropertyNotSupportedException.Adapter, NutNotFoundException, PollingOperationNotSupportedException, SaveOperationNotSupportedException, StaticWorkflowNotFoundException, StreamException, UnableToInstantiateException, WorkflowNotFoundException, WorkflowTemplateNotFoundException, WuicException, WuicRuntimeException, WuicXmlBadReferenceException, WuicXmlBadReferenceToDaoBuilderException, WuicXmlBadTypeOfValueException, WuicXmlException, WuicXmlMissingConfigurationElementException, WuicXmlNoAttributeException, WuicXmlNoClassAttributeException, WuicXmlNoConfigurationIdAttributeException, WuicXmlNoIdAttributeException, WuicXmlNoNutDaoBuilderClassAttributeException, WuicXmlNoNutDaoBuilderIdAttributeException, WuicXmlReadException, WuicXmlUnableToInstantiateException, WuicXmlWorkflowIdentifierException, WuicXmlWrappedErrorCodeException

    public interface ErrorCode

    All the error codes which identify the exceptions thrown by WUIC.
